d Strauss</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/roland-kluttig/" rel="tag">Roland Kluttig</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/salome/" rel="tag">Salome</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/shigeo-ishino/" rel="tag">Shigeo Ishino</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/simone-schneider/" rel="tag">Simone Schneider</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/staatsoper-stuttgart/" rel="tag">Staatsoper Stuttgart</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/torsten-hoffmann/" rel="tag">Torsten Hoffmann</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/yasin-el-harrouk/" rel="tag">Yasin El Harrouk</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Claudia Mahnke, Gergely Nemeti, Heinz Göhrig, Iain Paterson, Kirill Serebriannikov, Matthias Klink, Opera lirica, Pierre Jorge Gonzalez, Richard Strauss, Roland Kluttig, Salome, Shigeo Ishino, Simone Schneider, Staatsoper Stuttgart, Torsten Hoffmann, Yasin El Harrouk"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/e15610f34674f02caf174515ea5136d4" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2008/04/Mussomeli1-132x200.jpg" width="66" height="100" alt="Gianguido Mussomeli" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Gianguido Mussomeli"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/gianguido-mussomeli/">View all articles by Gianguido Mussomeli</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2015/11/operalombardia-teatro-fraschini-di-pavia-un-ballo-in-maschera/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> OperaLombardia, Teatro Fraschini di Pavia: &#8220;Un ballo in maschera&#8221;</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2015/11/pisa-teatro-verdi-il-convitato-di-pietra-2/" rel="next">Pisa, Teatro Verdi: &#8220;Il convitato di pietra&#8221; <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"></div></div></div></div><div id="secondary" class="widget-area span4 sb-4" role="complementary"> <aside id="search-4" class="widget widget_search clearfix"><h3 class="widget-title">RICERCA</h3><form method="get" id="searchform" action="http://www.gbopera.it/"> <label for="s" class="assistive-text">Search</label> <input type="text" class="field" name="s" id="s" placeholder="Search" /> <button type="submit" class="submit btn" name="submit" id="searchsubmit"><i class="icon-search"></i></button></form> </aside><aside id="ct-relatedposts-widget-2" class="widget ct-relatedposts-widget clearfix"><h3 class="widget-title">Articoli correlati</h3><ul class="related-posts-single clearfix"><li> <a href='http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/martina-franca-42-festival-della-valle-ditria-la-grotta-di-trofonio/' title='Martina Franca, 42° Festival della Valle d&#8217;Itria: &#8220;La grotta di Trofonio&#8221;'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/1K8A1319-70x70.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="la grotta di Trofonio, Martina Franca 2016" title="Martina Franca, 42° Festival della Valle d&#8217;Itria: &#8220;La grotta di Trofonio&#8221;" srcset="http://www.gbopera.